name: Morgan Dollar Pendant
description:
Mark Antonio Jewelry is proud to present the Morgan Dollar Pendant.

This item is made to order and may take up to 5 business days before it ships. If you need it sooner, please contact us.

Our pendants consist of coins with a 90% silver content.

Each coin used in our pendants is antique. We do not have any coins that were in circulation before 1890 or after 1945.

The chain is .925 Sterling with a rope design. 20 inches in length.
